cc:Work.dc:description:
This is a "classic" variant of the guyenne deck. Each figure occupies the whole card, leaving no space for the modern J-Q-K indication. This makes the cards more attractive and you still recognize the figures because each figure has its own specific characteristic: kings have a crown, jacks have a hat, queens wear a 'chador'. 
Suits are clearly color coded according to the "Turnierbild" used in Skat tournaments. 
 
this file works with gnome aisleriot 3.2.3.2.
